Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,GIVE ME CHOCOLATE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This society's all about Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You go around town, you see girls running left and right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,literally giving the candy companies their obscene profits!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But not one of those chocolates that are flying off the shelves will ever reach our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, not one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll never come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do? We don't have girlfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Valentine's Day is just some fictional event that happens in games and animes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll fly magically through the air or get attacked by an army of zombies before we get any chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit being so negative, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There might be a slight, miraculous, \NGod-only-knows, one-in-a-million chance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that one of us might get a box of chocolates containing the feelings... of a cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't make me feel better in the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:00:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then let's start practicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.68,0:01:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll imagine that we're getting Valentine's\N Day presents from cute girls as a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,si... shimi... shumi... what was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"Simulation".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that! We'll do it as simulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But how are we going to simulate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for example we could...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine you're getting one from Morishima-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.34,0:01:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting Valentine's Day \Nchocolates from Morishima-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are your Valentine's Day chocolates!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, don't be so grabby. I'll give it to you in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how you like me to feed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.32,0:01:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I make you say "Ahh"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mouth... to... mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Umehara...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure this will amount to any sort of "practice".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I have my doubts too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But we came this far so there's no turning back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, you act the part, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Ayatsuji-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I got you chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I made time in my busy schedule to go buy these for you, so be grateful when you eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,, make sure you yell out, "Thank you very much, Tsukasa-sama!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And kneel down before me sobbing while you eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're into?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayatsuji-san would never say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that wasn't what I was going for...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno, that just popped into my mind for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you're starting to get into this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually fun once you start doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now next up is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go with Sakurai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rihoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jun'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are your Valentine's Day chocolates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,These chocolates are really delicious, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones with the milk fillings are to die for!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... can I have a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I was the one who bought them anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, can you feed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to beat {\i1}my{\i0} power of imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not good enough, Umehara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, who're you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The number one cool beauty on the swim team, Nanasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:03:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Valentine's Day chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You said on our date that you love chocolate cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember all our memories we have together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy Valentine's Day, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That was sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing it cool with just a hint of dere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it {\i1}was{\i0} you playing her, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just replay that in your mind using her voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up next, Umehara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It better not be a half-hearted \Nfantasy or else you're not going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go with Tanamachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagining her won't do anything for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tada! Here are your chocolates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:05:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! These aren't leftovers from work like last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I splurged on these, so you better be thankful when eating them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a free kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Topping it off with a kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's beyond sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What say you? Did I win this showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're not done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have one last card left to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My last card...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is the one with the enchantingly soft \Nand squeezy body, Nakata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai? Here is your... Valentine's Day ch-chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked hard making it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be glad if you... like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:06:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A-And you also... have...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,another... present.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And th... that present is... me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That absolutely killed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving yourself as a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody thinks like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Umehara?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I won this match!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll manly own up to my defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You won, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, I applaud your fantasies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fantasies aren't half bad either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When did this turn into a fantasy showdown?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
